# Convex backend

- All backend code lives in repo-root `convex/` — not in apps or packages.
- After changing schema or functions, run `npm run convex:dev` to regenerate types.
- Client code imports API via `@counseliq/admin/db/api` or `@counseliq/client/db/api` — do not import `_generated` directly from apps.
- Auth mutations live in `convex/auth.ts`; schema in `convex/schema.ts`.
- Do not edit files in `convex/_generated/`.
- **User-facing failures:** throw `appError(AppErrorCode.X)` from `convex/errors.ts` — not plain `Error` or string `ConvexError`. Add new codes to `AppErrorCode` and map them in product package error message files.
